# Frontend ‚Äî Portfolio

> Full reference: `TECH_CONVENTIONS.md`

## Layout

```
src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ alignment/     # mini-game (desktop md+)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/    # sections + shared/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ constants/     # shared copy/data
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ contexts/      # providers in App.tsx / index.tsx
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ hooks/         # shared hooks
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ motion/        # shared motion helpers
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ types/         # cross-feature enums/types
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ utils/         # shared utils (cn)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ App.tsx
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ index.css
```

**Colocate** hooks, utils, constants, types, and contexts with their owner. Promote to top-level folders only when reused across unrelated features, or when a provider mounts in `App.tsx` / `index.tsx`. Component-specific types stay in that component folder (e.g. `Button.type.ts`).

## Code

- No `any`. Props: `ComponentNameProps`. Fixed-choice inputs ‚Üí **enum** (not string unions).
- Cross-feature enums/types ‚Üí `src/types/`. Component enums ‚Üí co-located `*.type.ts`.
- Props order: required ‚Üí optional; vars ‚Üí callbacks; alphabetical within each group (types, destructuring, JSX).
- Imports: external ‚Üí internal ‚Üí relative ‚Üí assets. Named exports; barrel from `components/shared`.
- Copy in `*.const.ts` ‚Äî not hardcoded in components. Reuse `components/shared/` and `Section`.
- Tailwind + semantic tokens (`ink`, `bg`, `accent`, `line`). Theme via `ThemeProvider` in `src/contexts`.
- `useCallback` / `useMemo` only when justified. No `console.log`.

## New section checklist

